messages.message:
Interesting reading about onboarding customers which I think we should look at: https://wraptext.equals.com/why-you-should-add-friction-to-your-onboarding.
_“The thing people misunderstand about onboarding is the goal is not for people to complete onboarding. Your goal is for people to get their first moments of *value from your product*, commonly known as “*activation*”. All the talk about eliminating friction and removing steps is totally detached from this goal._”
